{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileInfoSignalName\/notify"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileInfoSignalName"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_set()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"symbolKind":"case","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:3GIO18FileInfoSignalNameO6notifyyA2CmF","title":"FileInfoSignalName.notify","roleHeading":"Case"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/fileinfosignalname\/notify"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"notify"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"text":" results","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"code":"notify","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify()"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_signal_connect()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"C","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"It is important to note that you must use","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" as"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"detail strings for the notify signal."}]}]}],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names":{"type":"link","titleIn